# BhanksToken (BHNK)

## Overview
BHNK is the native utility and governance token
of the Bhanks Base ecosystem.

## Details
- Name: BhanksToken
- Symbol: BHNK
- Standard: ERC-20
- Network: Base
- Initial supply: 1,000,000 BHNK

## Utility
- Governance: Vote on BhanksDAO proposals
- Staking: Stake BHNK to earn rewards
- Access: Future utility TBD

## Distribution
- 100% minted to deployer on launch
- Community airdrops planned
- No VC allocation
- No presale

## Contract
Deployed on Base Sepolia testnet.
Mainnet deployment coming in v1.1.